  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1035">
<l>iravā rirappārkkoṉ ṟīvar karavātu</l>
<l>kaiceytūṇ mālai yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those whose nature is to live by manual labour will never beg but give something to those who beg.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
